who made the river such a special place for so many. Happy memories were made here, and they will forever be in our thoughts as we make new ones."┼
┬IN MEMORY OF A MUCH LOVED BROTHER
DOUGIE CANT
WHO DID 03.12.3019 AGED 84

IN MEMORY OF A MUCH LOVED BROTHER
RODDY CANT
