╔IN MEMORY OF OUR DAUGHTER
CHARLOTTE HELLEBRANDT
29.12..92 - 26. 10. 95
YOU CAME TO VISIT, NOT TO STAY
JUST TO LEAD US ON OUR WAY
YOUR MEMORY WILL SHINE A LIGHT
UNTIL THE DAY WE REUNITE

CHRISTINA HELLEBRANDT
16-11-1966 TO 12-11-2000
AT PEACE NOW WITH HER BELOVED CHARLOTTE (MAY THE WINDS OF LOVE SURROUND YOU). 
R.I.P."╠
